text: INSEAD (Institut européen d'administration des affaires) is an European higher studies establishment. The school is in 3 places, in Fontainebleau, France, in Abu Dhabi and in Singapore.Pour les MBA, "l'Insead est une véritable école globale " INSEAD is specialist in the fields of economics, social sciences and management. ==References== == Further reading == * INSEAD website Category:Education in France
